text: Lars-Åke Lindqvist (born 13 October 1959) is a Swedish rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Sweden Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
